  `groupContext.groupId` (RFC 9420 H4), closing a cross-group replay hole where a signed
  external-sender proposal (or any other message) for group A could be replayed verbatim into
  group B.
- Found this story's fix already drafted, uncommitted, in the working tree at session start
  (`src/process-messages.ts`, `test/index.ts` modified; `test/scenario/cross-group-replay.ts`
  untracked). This session's REASONING note said the task had "stalled once already" -- consistent
