  - `src/process-messages.ts`: `processPrivateMessage` now checks
    `constantTimeEqual(pm.groupId, state.groupContext.groupId)` and `processPublicMessage` checks
    `constantTimeEqual(pm.content.groupId, state.groupContext.groupId)`, each as the very first
    statement in the function -- before the epoch check, before any decrypt/unprotect call -- and
