  - Verified TDD properly despite the code being pre-drafted: `git stash push -- src/process-messages.ts`
    (kept the new test file and the `test/index.ts` registration), reran via the single-file
    esbuild-bundle recipe from Codebase Patterns -- got 19 failing assertions (one per ciphersuite,
    "group B rejects a proposal replayed from group A" failing because `processPublicMessage`
    happily accepted the cross-group message pre-fix). `git stash pop` restored the fix; all 57
    assertions passed post-fix.
