    'application' && groupContext.epoch !== 0n` for any PSK ID in the list. Wired into two call
    sites: (1) `validateProposals` (member-commit path, used by both sender-side `createCommit` and
    receiver-side `processCommit`), right after the existing duplicate-PskId check; (2) directly in
